These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: scientific, western
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific  | western |
| Transport     | taxi | quad-bike  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: peach, garlic
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, basketball
1. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | peach      | garlic         |
| Sport   | surfing | basketball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea
There 2 different types of food: lettuce, carrot
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person eating carrot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | tea | coffee   |
| Food       | carrot  | lettuce |

 #################################

 
